---
title: Hoisin Prawn Noodles with ginger and courgette
description: Ginger and lime are a delicious addition to the crunchy veg and sweet and meaty prawns in this super simple recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_R04_W17_IE_IEXCFS0066-4_Main_high-e26fd10f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/hoisin-prawn-noodles-63d8df51dd4a18d65316b026-08ce27dc.pdf
